Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dracula前情提要\NPreviously on Dracula...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaw将军是无辜的\NGeneral Shaw is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我毁了他  是你\NI didn't destroy the man. You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan不在这\NJonathan's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信如果你要\NI'm sure you'll have no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,重新找一个舞伴并不是什么难事\Ntrouble finding another partner to dance with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你 Mina\NI love you, Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,呃... 你该走了\NEhm... you need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,该有人教教她什么是痛苦\NSomeone should teach her such pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我会教你怎么捕获Jonathan的心\NI will teach you how to haunt Jonathan's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我进行了实验\NI conducted an experiment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把这种物质\Nby adding this substance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,注入人类面颊的细胞\Nto human cheek cells,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而那些死亡细胞复活了\Nand the dead cells reanimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\NLadies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这台机器危害了公共安全\Nthis machine is a threat to public safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙会烧死了我的妻儿\NThe Order burnt my wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们粉身碎骨之时\NYou will have your revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是你我报仇雪恨之时\NWhen we crush them, we both will.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的血清\NWith your serum,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以在阳光下行走\NI can walk in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是仅限于四个小时之内\NBut it will only allow you four hours in daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 其他人会怎么说? - 什么人?\N- What would people say? - What people?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手在抖\NYour hands are trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你究竟爱谁 Alexander Grayson?\NSo who do you love most, Alexander Grayson?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不!\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不!\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(278.4,276.574)}先生 能问个问题么?\NSir, may I ask a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(262.4,275.861)}如果我告诉你不能\NIf I told you no,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你会不问么?\Nwould it stop you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不会\NProbably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算在这里坐多久?\NHow long do you intend to sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生... - 我允许提问\N- Sir... - I allowed a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但不代表我会回答\NThat does not mean I wish to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有种愚蠢叫做痴迷\NThere is folly in this obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢且致命\NFolly and threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要一个女孩\NIf you want the girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去争夺\Nthen take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你不能拥有\NBut if you cannot have her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就放手\Nthen walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\NEnough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"争夺她  或放她走"\N"Take her, or walk away."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,若真有如此简单\NIf only it was that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,前者会把Mina置于危险之中\NThe first would put Mina in mortal danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,至于后者...\NBut the second...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,会让我生不如死\NThat would be the end of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你在这做什么?\NFather. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我来接你回家\NI've come to grab you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不工作到这么晚\NI don't work this late
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我才是个医师\Nand I actually am a physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是...我有些东西要...\NI just... I have a few more things that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,躲在这里 躲着我\NHiding here, avoiding me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,躲着Jonathan\Navoiding Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有躲着任何人\NI'm not avoiding anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 让我说完\NNo, no. Let me speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个美国人对你来说是什么?\NWhat is the American to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱Jonathan\NI love Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从小青梅竹马 而且...\NI have known him my entire life, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他就像我的一个家人\NWell, he's like family to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他会成为我的丈夫\NHe will be my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而我会成为他的妻子\Nand I will be his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 告诉我 Mina\NBut, tell me, Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是Alexander...\NBut Alexander...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他身上散发着一种...\NHe exerts a kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,磁铁般的引力\NMagnetic force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不论我多么努力的尝试\NAnd no matter how hard I try,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不能...\NI can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来我就像一个傻瓜\NI sound like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是这样的\NNo, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我过去的生命中\NI loved one woman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也爱过一个女人\Nin my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我和你母亲之间\NBut my path to your mother
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也是起起伏伏\Nwas hardly a straight line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我做了\NSo I did the only possible thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一能得到幸福的抉择\Nwhen it comes to happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,随心之所向\NI followed my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,黑荒原 船头\NBlackheath, bow,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Islington 还有Chelsea\NIslington, and Chelsea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,四个  昨天晚上\NFour. Tracked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,已经全部被消灭\Nand exterminated this last evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢上帝\NGood God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以得出一个不容置疑的论断\NWe can only draw one inescapable conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你如何否认?\NHow can you deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的现象都很明显\NThe signs are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦现在有另一个年长的吸血鬼\NThere is another elder vampire in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你说过\NBut you said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经杀死了年长的吸血鬼\Nyou'd killed the old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 但是祸患还在继续\NI did. But the plague continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,当年长的吸血鬼死去\NWhere the old one goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那么他的血裔也会相继死去\Nthe sons and daughters follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这里还有一个\NThere is another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去吧\NThen go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,找到他 干掉他\NFind it and destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,美好的夜晚 对吧?\NLovely night, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在才开始\NIt is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次吧 从你的脸上看得出来\NFirst time, by the looks of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么看出来的? - 别担心...\N- How can you tell? - Not to worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladybird会照顾好每件事的\NLadybird'll take care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哦! 见鬼!\NOh! Bloody hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以流言是真的\NSo the rumors are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真有一个猎人\NA proper huntsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还是一个女人\NAnd a woman, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候去死了\NIt's time to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太晚了 已经 死过了\NToo late. Already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谁召你来的\NWho called you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们的主人 - 名字\N- Our master. - Name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他有很多 - 我不喜欢猜谜\N- He has many. - I'm not a fan of riddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 名字 - 他会杀了我的\N- Name. - He will destroy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 名字 - 堕落者\N- Name. - The Fell One.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子\NLiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Vlad Tepes 穿刺者\NVlad Tepes. Vlad the Impaler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dracula\NDracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不可能 - 我们誓死效忠于他\N- It cannot be. - We swarm to do his bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,万众齐心 我们就会制造出\NTogether, we will make
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,永无止境的黑暗\Nan endless night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他的巢穴在哪?\NWhere's his nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我!\NTell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都会告诉你的\NI'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(271.467,242.356)\c&HEA57B9&\4c&HA2955F&\fn华文行楷\fs24\i1}翻译：格  三文鱼
