Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HEA57B9&\4c&HA2955F&\fn华文行楷\fs24\i1\pos(118.4,218.118)}校对  监制：幸福ing形式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HEA57B9&\4c&HA2955F&\fn华文行楷\fs24\i1\pos(203.2,206.712)}德  古  拉  \N第一季第八集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn楷体\fs24\i1\pos(190.4,220.97)\3c&H000000&\4c&H1CB1B3&\c&HFFFFFF&}真 爱 字 幕 组\N——— 出 品 ———
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有麻烦了 - 什么麻烦?\N- I'm in trouble. - What kind of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,发誓这事不会有第三个人知道\NSwear to me this stays between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓不会告诉任何人\NI swear I will tell no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(124.267,275.861)}关于Shaw的事情\NThe story about Shaw
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(118.933,271.584)}是彻头彻尾的谎言\Nwas a complete fabrication.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(112.533,275.149)}那么那些证据呢?\NWhat about the evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(112,271.584)}他的财务记录...\NHis financial records...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(120,268.733)}假的 一丝一毫都是假的\NFaked. Every shred of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么做?\NWhy would you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\NI didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有 是Grayson\NI didn't. It was Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他策划了整件事情\NHe engineered the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那就撤出来\NSo retract it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能  Grayson把自己\NI can't. Grayson was too clever
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,撇的一干二净\Nto get his hands dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一定有什么人能证实\NThere must be someone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你所说的一切\Nwho can corroborate your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那个会计? - 她不见了\N- The bookkeeper? - She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她就凭空消失了\NShe's disappeared into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没人再在白天见过她\NNo one's seen her in days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得Grayson可能会...\NYou think Grayson might have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的...\NYou know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么?  - 让她消失?\N- What? - Made her disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你现在有危险了么?\NDo you think you're in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这样\NThen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着  你可能会用到的\NTake this. You may need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的太过了\NYou've outdone yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没想到过\NI never thought
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你会愚蠢到去屠杀\Nyou'd be stupid enough to slaughter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,苏格兰的警察总督\NChief Inspector of Scotland Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找到真相  而且找到了\NI wanted the truth and I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  这我确信\NYes, I'm certain you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉了我整个的阴谋\NHe told me the entire plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们给所有人都下了毒\NThey poisoned all those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是恶龙会\NIt's the Order of the Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么好意外的?\NIt surprises you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这证明我们的技术\NIt proves our technology
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,和此毫无关系\Nhad nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样\NIt doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙会会使我们的共振器\NThe Order made it look like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来就是有问题\Nit was our resonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在大众的眼里\NIn the public's eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,它是不安全的  致命的\Nit is unsafe, deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那就会是他们唯一记得的事情\NThat is all they know and all they will remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,即使机器被证实是无可非议的\NEven if the technology is proven blameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,都结束了  我们完了\NIt's finished. We are ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那你觉得我们该怎么办?\NAnd what do you suggest we do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃?\NGive up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们辛苦做了这么多以后?\NAfter all our hard work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不会放弃\NNo, I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去复仇\NI will have my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你会报仇雪恨的 当我...\NYou will have your revenge when I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了?\NReady?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么?\NWhat were you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我们去证明\NYou were saying we will prove
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,机器是无害的\Nthe technology is harmless
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然后继续原来的计划\Nand continue as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dracula是一个传说\NDracula is a myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是吓唬不听话的孩子的故事\NA tale told to frighten children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经失去理智了么?\NHave you taken leave of your senses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个安静\NBe quiet, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信我  是吗?\NYou believe me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾是一个人类\NHe was a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字是Vlad Tepes  穿刺者\NHis name was Vlad Tepes, Vlad the Impaler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是中世纪的战士王子\NHe was a medieval warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,以野蛮残酷而闻名\Nprince renowned for his savagery and ruthlessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,曾是他的地区的首席猎人\NHe was master huntsman in his native land,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他曾效命于\Nand he served on the High Council
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个组织的高级委员会\Nof this very organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这太荒唐了  - 真荒谬\N- This is absurd. - It's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她是对的  是有过这样一个人\NShe's right. There was such a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有关他的文字记载都被禁涉\NThe texts concerning him are forbidden to all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是龙之会的领导人\Nbut the Dragon's heads
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和首席猎人知晓\Nand their chief huntsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他无视龙之会\NHe defied the Ordo Draco,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,被逐出了教会\Nwas excommunicated by the Church
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,被判为有罪的异端\Nand found guilty of heresy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他罪大恶极以至于\NSo grievous was his sin that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,死刑已经不够作为刑罚\Na sentence of death was considered inadequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们举行神秘的仪式\NSo they employed occult rituals and transformed him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,把他转化为永生的恶魔\Ninto the living demon that we now know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是我们都知道的堕落者\Nas the Fell One,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nosferatu  吸血鬼始祖\NNosferatu, primo Master vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dracula\NDracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不是被转化的\NCreated, not sired,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们创造的\Nby us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么证据证明\NWhat proof do you have that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他在伦敦?\Nhe's in London?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他毁掉我的先知\NHe swatted off my seers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就如同踩死蝼蚁一般\Nlike flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他轻易就打败了Kruger\NHe easily bested Kruger,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在我麾下的\None of the most formidable huntsmen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,最强大的猎人之一\NI've ever had under my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他能躲避侦查\NHe's avoided detection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他和那些听命于他的血裔\NHe's infested London
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在为祸伦敦\Nwith creatures answering his call,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是最终  昨晚\Nand finally, last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个已明确的说出他的名字\None of them explicitly named him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那我估计他在委员会面前也会说的\NAnd I presume it would do the same before the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  她应该会\NWell, she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,前提是她没有被我的枪爆头\NHad she not taken my weapon and blown her own head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,多么巧合\NHow very convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他是对的\NHe's right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你的猜想也许是真的  但是\NYour suspicions may be true, but we cannot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能仅凭一个\Nrely on the word
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那种东西的一面之词\Nof one of those creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要证据  如山的铁证\NBring us proof. Compelling proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是唯一能让这种说法\NIt's the only way such a claim
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,使人信服的方式\Ncan be believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果Dracula真在伦敦\NIf Dracula's in London,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我一定会找到他\Nsir, I will find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我会一次解决掉他们\NI will end him once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan\NJonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你同意...\NYou agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之间不该有秘密的对吧?\NThat there should be no secrets between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是Grayson\NIt's Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么了?\NWhat about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他当着我的面说谎\NHe lied to my face,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就为了破坏\Nin order to destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaw将军的名誉\Nthe reputation of General Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但是Jonathan  你说过...\NBut Jonathan, you said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  Mina\NPlease, Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,请你听我说完\NJust please, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson勒索了Laurent勋爵\NGrayson blackmailed Lord Laurent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在Laurent就死了\Nand now Laurent's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就像还年轻的Davenport一样\Nas is young Davenport,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,都是他搞出来的\Nand by his own hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是报纸不是这样说的\NThat's not what the papers said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他会不惜一切手段\NHe will do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,去建成他的项目\Nin the pursuit of his grand project.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,勒索  诽谤...\NBlackmail, slander...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知  还有谋杀\NAnd for all I know, murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谋杀?\NMurder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我见过的最邪恶的人\NHe's the closest thing to evil I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan...\NJonathan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mina...  - 如果这是真的...\N- Mina... - If this is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么还要继续为他效力呢?\NThen why do you continue in his employ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我有我的理由\NI have my reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 而且是好理由  - 没有秘密\N- And good ones. - No secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,求你 给我点时间\NPlease, just give me time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我会解释所有事情\Nand I will explain everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在那之前...\NBut until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那之前\NUntil then,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要远离Alexander Grayson\Nyou stay away from Alexander Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想见她  Jenkins\N- I want to see her, Jenkins,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,让我进去\Nlet me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jayne女士外出了 先生\NLady Jayne is traveling, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道她在这  让我进去\NI know she's here. Let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenkins  让他进来\NJenkins, let him in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander  你的突然到来\NAlexander, how lovely of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,多让人开心\Nto drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  Jenkins  没事了\NThank you, Jenkins, that will be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要我\NIf you need me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 随时叫我  - 好的\N- just call. - I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NExcuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不记得有邀请你\NI don't remember inviting you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从没正式见过面吧？\NWe've never stood on formality, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这干什么  Alexander？\NWhy are you here, Alexander?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道为什么  - 嗯  我知道\N- You know why. - Yes, yes I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧你赢了\NYou win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都结束了  Alexander\NIt's over, Alexander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我会承认的\NI'll admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经看到了我的结果\NI have met my match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想听这个吗？\NIs that what you want to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你打败我了\NYou have bested me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  请出去\NNow, please, just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经没有时间继续玩这个游戏了\NI'm far too busy to continue playing this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏？\NGame?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧  收手吧好吗\NOh, please, just stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我用我的生命来保护你\NI risked my life to protect yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是  没错\NYes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我无论如何也搞不明白\NAnd for the life of me, I can't work out why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你的竟然芳心他许了\NYour heart clearly belongs to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候知道的？\NWhen did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,自从你跟她…\NWhen you danced with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在她订婚舞会上一起跳舞\NAt her engagement party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么明显吗？\NWas it that obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说  太明显不过了\NTo me, glaringly so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生\NMr. Grayson...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,总是Mina  对么\NIt was always Mina,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候跟我在一起过？\Nwasn't it, when you were with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你说谎\NYou're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你想告诉我点什么呢？\NSo, what have you got to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了一些人\NI found some men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NMm-mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人  可靠吗？\NThese men, are they reliable?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  非常可靠  是的\NMm-mmm, very much so, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 开个价吧  - 好\N- For a price. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你要做的就是介绍一下他们\NNow all you need to do is introduce them
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,给这个充满疑问的女士\Nto the lady in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我得多久之后再介绍呢？\NAnd how soon will I start making these introductions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,越快越好\NThe sooner the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我要杀哪只？\NWho do I have to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不如别杀了吧  先生？\NMay I suggest no one, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也许只有这一次呢\NPerhaps just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真相不会大白的话\NIf the truth won't set the resonator free,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有人要继续牺牲了\Nperhaps someone's excised heart will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我有那些当官的名单\NI have the name of a bureaucrat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为了健康  我确信\Non the Board of Health, who I am assured
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我能接受适度的自由\Nwill be most accommodating for a very modest fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  贿赂那些蛀虫吧\NFine, bribe the worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果必须的话\NA king's ransom,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一个国王的赎金\Nif you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果不成功的话\NBut if it doesn't succeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就按照我的方法来\Nthen we do it my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了\NUnderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  抱歉\NSorry, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,男管家让我进来的\Nthe butler let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Murray小姐  真的好巧啊\NMiss Murray, what a pleasant surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield\NRenfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟Jonathan谈过话了\NI've spoken with Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他看起来很不安\NHe seemed quite terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么？  - 因为你\N- By what? - By you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真荒谬\NThat's preposterous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是么？  - 当然了\N- Is it? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟Jonathan一样了解我\NYou know me as long as Jonathan has.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我让你不安了吗？  - 没有…\N- Do I terrify you? - No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我一点都不了解你\NBut I don't know you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,恰恰相反  Murray小姐\NOn the contrary, Miss Murray,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你比任何其他人\NI would venture that you know me better
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都要了解我\Nthan anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅我\NForgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常\NI sometimes give voice to things
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,言常人所不敢言\Nthat are better left unsaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要道歉了\NNo, don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我最欣赏你的一点\NIt's what I like most about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,美国人  你的真诚\NAmericans. Your honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远不会对你撒谎\NI will never lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\NYou have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么Jonathan那么不安？\NWhy was Jonathan so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina  有个很有权势的人\NMina, there are powerful men
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,希望阻止我\Nwho wish to stop me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是实际上  我必须去与\Nbut on occasion, I have to match
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的无情竞争\Ntheir ruthlessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不然的话未来将一片黯淡\Nor the future will be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要犯错误了  Mina\NMake no mistake, Mina,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker现在的无情跟我有一比了\NHarker's proving to be as ruthless as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  比你更甚\NOn occasion, more so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  你错了  - 有么？\N- No, you're wrong. - Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan是对的\NJonathan was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你感染了人们\NYou infect people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你称之为魅力\NYou call it charm,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些都只是你为了自己的私利\Nbut it's all for your own self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan和我不会再被你所用了\NJonathan and I will not be used up by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一个标准的英国绅士应该\NA proper English gentleman must have
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在婚礼上有个完整的英国背心\Na proper English waistcoat on his wedding day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是首先\Nbut first,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他必须要有个合适的衣服\None must select the appropriate fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我有调色板\NI have swatches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy  我觉得这个调色非常重要\NLucy, I'm sure the swatches are very important,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我真的不能耽误工作  所以…\Nbut I really can't be late for work, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点也不关心什么狗屁的调色…\NI don't care a damn about the swatches...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  你会在这\NThen why... why are you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是调色板的事的话？\Nif not for the swatches?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你会觉得我是个傻瓜\NYou'll think me a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy…\NLucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我来着是因为我一直在想你\NI came here because I can't get you out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直拘束着我的情感\NI keep my feelings close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来都是这样\NI always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,太多  以至于你完全没有\NSo much so, you seem entirely
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,察觉到他们\Nunaware of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样多久…\NHow long have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候开始……\Nwhen did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我没预见到这个也没有计划过\NI neither planned nor expected this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  我们现在在这\Nand yet, here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我\NYou and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy…\NLucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么  最终都会过去的\NWhatever this is, it will pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  如果仅仅是看着Mina的份上的话\NIt must, if only for Mina's sake. Mina,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都爱着她\Nwhom we both love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的对  当然\NYou're right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望我能得到你的力量\NI only wish I had your strength of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不说这个了好吗\NLet's not speak of this again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看在Mina的份上\Nfor Mina's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  这只是行动的一部分\NYes, that is the only course of action,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全同意\NI completely agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一个决定\NOne condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,给我个吻帮我度过这个难关\NA kiss to help me after.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不要  这是不可能的\NNo, no, that's... that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,承认我的安慰吧\NDo not deny me this consolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对于我遭受的痛苦来说\NIt's a small crumb to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是很小的一部分\Nease the pain of all that I shall never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一个吻而已\NOne kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友之间的一个吻\NA kiss between friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你人很好  你也很慷慨\NYou're kind. And you're generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不不\NNo, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能不遵守对Mina的约定\NI cannot break my promise to Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina\NMina.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩是该有多高兴啊\NHow happy you both must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,总是在一起\NAlways together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是你在庄园工作的时候\Neven when you're working at Carfax Manor,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她也经常拜访你\Nshe's always visiting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊？\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天见她了\NI saw her there yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,上个星期也是\Nlast week as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她都形成习惯了\NShe does make a habit of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她因为你才去拜访的  不是吗？\NIt was you she was visiting, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina Murray在审判我！\NMina Murray judges me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她嘲笑我！\NShe scorns me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她从来没有原谅过我！\NShe will not forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要点血\NI want some blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.12,0:22:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让你离开这个庄园\NI can't let you leave Carfax Manor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不能这么出去\Nnot like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁能挡我？  - 我能\N- Who will stop me? - I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要血！\NI want blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield  看在你自己的份上\NRenfield, for your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina Murray已经扎根在你心里了\NMina Murray's taken root in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:22:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她的存在\NHer existence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:22:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只能使你的本性难以抑制\Nonly makes your true nature harder to disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她让你开始讨厌自己的本质--Dracula\NShe makes you hate the one thing you are - Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是要不是Dracula\NBut without Dracula,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不可能打败恶龙会\Nyou can never defeat the Ordo Draco.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底该怎么做？\NWhat am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了她或者得到她\NForget her or take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.85,0:23:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你离他远一点\NI told you to stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的我知道\NYes, I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我只是试着寻找真相\Nbut I was only trying to uncover the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你事实\NI told you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.59,0:23:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是  当然  但是我想知道…\NYes, of course, but I wanted to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得Grayson的话比我的可靠？\NAnd you take Grayson's word over mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.38,0:23:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这一段时间  我装作没看见\NThis whole time, I tried not to see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在就发生在我眼前\Nand it was right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看见什么？\NSee what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你和Grayson  - 你怎么敢\N- You and Grayson. - How dare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.72,0:23:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我去那是去保护你\NI went there to protect you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而你却做最坏的猜想\Nand you assume the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,之前呢？\NAnd the time before?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有幅照片\NThere was a phonograph,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在医院跳舞时候照的\Nfor the dance at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.92,0:23:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 总是有理由\N- There's always a reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.92,0:23:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧？  - 是  很好的理由\Nisn't there? - Yes, a very good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.42,0:23:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是你故意让它们发生的\NOr do you just invent them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:23:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你就有理由去见他了\Nso you have an excuse to see him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:23:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他去调情？\Nto flirt with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我从来没有\NNo, I would never even...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信你！\NI don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次问你\NFor the last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么跟自己\Nwhy must you make this
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.51,0:24:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这么过不去呢？\Nso difficult for yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.07,0:24:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪？\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.08,0:24:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是圣水\NIt's holy water.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.45,0:24:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你渴么？  - 你问啥  我说啥\N- Are you thirsty? - If you ask, I'll answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.39,0:24:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Dracula在哪？  - 我不知道\N- Where is Dracula? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.39,0:25:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没人看见过他\NNo one sees him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.33,0:25:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说他能在白天出没\NAnd they say he lives in the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.86,0:25:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不可能的\NThat's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.36,0:25:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到的就是这个\NIt's what I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.89,0:25:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他不需要夜幕的遮掩了\NHe has no need for the blanket of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.46,0:25:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对他来说  太阳\NFor him, the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.93,0:25:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是另外一个星星而已\Nis just another star.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.59,0:25:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,离得远近  没有任何区别\NClose or far away, it makes no difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.38,0:25:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他超越了上帝\NHe has bested God.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.78,0:25:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么超越的？\NHow?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.09,0:25:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,跟如何有关系吗？\NWhat does it matter how?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.49,0:25:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,事实就是这样的\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.79,0:25:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你会因他的愤怒而害怕\NYou will fear his wrath by day,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.53,0:25:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,无论白天还是黑夜\Nby night,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.35,0:25:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你永远不会看见他的到来\Nand you will never see him coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.76,0:25:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,15年小心翼翼的计划\N15 years of meticulous planning,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.67,0:25:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,用大量财富发展起来的技术\NA fortune developing a technology
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.07,0:25:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,去破坏他们的石油利润\Nto undermine their petroleum interests,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.27,0:25:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,使其浪费\Nwasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.05,0:25:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们还有选择  - 选择？\N- We still have options. - Options?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.70,0:26:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,教授  你真的应该\NProfessor, you really
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.27,0:26:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下来然后冷静一下\Nshould take a seat and try to calm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.03,0:26:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你已经跟那些官僚\NTell me you've made some progress
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.32,0:26:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,取得进展了\Nwith these bureaucrats?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.39,0:26:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所有的关系\NEvery contact
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.84,0:26:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,都将我们的预算视而不见\Nwe've had has ignored our advances.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.16,0:26:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这就像我们被冻结\NIt's as if we've been frozen out
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.60,0:26:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后从顶上摔下来\Nfrom the top down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.60,0:26:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这个人  Browning…  - Browning？\N- This man, Browning... - Browning?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.02,0:26:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  看起来他运用了\NYes, he seems to exert an
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.86,0:26:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,铁腕手段控制了伦敦的政治集团\Niron grip over London's political machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.80,0:26:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他在Grayson先生的黑名单里面\NHe's on Mr. Grayson's short list.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.46,0:26:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,最高委员会\NDefinitely High Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.09,0:26:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他也许就是恶龙会的首领\NHe may even be the Dragon's Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.02,0:26:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.72,0:26:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸  爸爸  爸爸！\NPapa, papa, papa, papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.59,0:26:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.83,0:26:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他吗？\NDo you know of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.62,0:27:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我从未听说过这个男人\NNo, I've never heard of this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.40,0:28:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗？\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.50,0:28:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你想干什么？\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.12,0:28:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这干什么？\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.81,0:28:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  Murray小姐\NHello, Miss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.99,0:28:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,多美好的夜晚啊  是不是？\NQuite a lovely night, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.16,0:28:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  呃…\NAh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.16,0:28:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在  现在  - 啊！\N- Now, now. - Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.49,0:28:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢有勇气的女孩\NI like a girl with spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.74,0:29:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但只是点到为止\NBut only to a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.54,0:29:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  我保证你没见过\NNow, I'm assuming that you've never seen
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.40,0:29:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,硫酸滴在人脸上是什么样子的\Nwhat sulfuric acid does to a body's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.85,0:29:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,它直接穿过皮肤  就像…\NIt eats right through the skin, just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.32,0:29:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,火穿过纸一样\NFire through paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.17,0:29:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴唇和眼睑…\NLips and lids...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.03,0:29:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,烧掉\NBurn right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.99,0:29:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,把鼻子变成两个洞洞\NTurns the nose into nothing but a couple of holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.73,0:29:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看好了学着点  先生们\NWatch and learn, gents.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.63,0:29:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看准了好好学\NWatch and learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.10,0:30:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,弗拉德三世\NVlad the Impaler.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.97,0:30:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,德古拉\NDracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.94,0:30:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她受的大部分是皮外伤\NHer injuries are largely superficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.99,0:30:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她会好起来的  Jonathan\NShe will be fine, Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.43,0:31:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁会做这种事？  - 我不知道\N- Who could have done this? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.80,0:31:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她会恢复吗？\NWill she recover?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.42,0:31:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她会的\NShe will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.12,0:31:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,医生\NDoctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.58,0:31:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina\NMina.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.14,0:31:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina\NMina.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.24,0:31:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谁做的？\NWho did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.62,0:31:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina\NMina.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.58,0:31:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这很重要\NIt's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.84,0:31:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要告诉我们一切\NYou must tell us everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.06,0:31:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有仨男人...\NThere were three men...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.39,0:31:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们袭击了我\NAnd they attacked me
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.78,0:32:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,并把我按在了桌子上。\Nand held me on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.78,0:32:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,太快了  我记不住了\NIt was so fast. I can't... I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.28,0:32:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谁？  是谁做的？\NWho? Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.82,0:32:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他拿着一个瓶子\NHe had a bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.10,0:32:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一瓶硫酸  - 额  天那。\N- A bottle of acid. - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.50,0:32:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他有一块胎记\NAnd a birthmark,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.81,0:32:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他的脸上有块焰色记\Na port wine stain on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.93,0:32:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 额  天那  - 谁啊？\N- Oh, my God. - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.86,0:32:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是警察  - 什么...？\N- The police. - Yes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.39,0:32:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,必须马上通知他们\NThey must be informed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.54,0:32:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan...\NJonathan...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.33,0:32:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Harker！- 你要干什么？\N- Harker! - What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.55,0:32:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你一样  公平\NI want the same thing you do, justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.20,0:32:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要你的帮助\NI don't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.56,0:32:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是  你不要\NNo, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.52,0:32:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个有胎记的男人\NThe man with the birthmark,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.45,0:32:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫Hackett\Nhis name is Hackett.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.42,0:32:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hackett是Davenport的人\NHackett's Davenport's man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.68,0:33:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须警告有关当局\NI must alert the proper authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.41,0:33:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,警告他们？\NAlert them?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.34,0:33:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 真的吗？\N- Yes. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.14,0:33:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你要告诉他们Davenport勋爵\NYou're gonna tell them Lord Davenport
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.91,0:33:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让他的手下\Nsent his man
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.75,0:33:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,用硫酸袭击你的未婚妻？\Nto attack your fiancee with acid?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.59,0:33:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的。\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.72,0:33:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一位集财富和声誉的\NHe is a well-respected man
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.49,0:33:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,备受敬仰的人\Nof wealth and reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.42,0:33:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,警察往往对那样的人从轻处理\NPolice tend to treat men like that lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.61,0:33:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们一定知道真相  - 真相？\N- They must know the truth. - The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.01,0:33:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的观点\NIt's your word,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.08,0:33:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一个前新闻工作者\Nan ex-journalist,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.41,0:33:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,和一个上议院的贵族对抗\Nagainst a peer of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.22,0:33:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你觉得他们会相信谁呢？\NCome on. Who do you think they're going to believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.38,0:33:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我会亲自问他的\NWell, then I'll ask him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.53,0:33:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Davenport是不会骗我的\NDavenport won't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.15,0:33:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会在乎他有多少钱\NI don't care how much money he has,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.73,0:33:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让他开口的\NI'll make him answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.25,0:34:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,额  Harker先生\NAh, Mr. Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.23,0:34:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我真相\NTell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.92,0:34:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,实在抱歉  我还不知道\NSorry, I haven't an earthly idea
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.80,0:34:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在说什么\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.89,0:34:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你的人  Hackett\NYour man, Hackett.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.13,0:34:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他袭击了Mina\NHe attacked Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.65,0:34:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是对Shaw将军的报复\NThis was retaliation for General Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.15,0:34:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么对一个无辜的女人\NHow dare you go after
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.00,0:34:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,下此毒手？\Nan innocent woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.90,0:34:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  小男孩\NListen, dear boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.32,0:34:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不知道\NI don't know anything about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.42,0:34:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Murray小姐  她还好么？\NMiss Murray, is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.37,0:34:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谁送你来的？\NWho sent you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.44,0:34:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没人\NNo one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.14,0:34:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不  是Grayson  是不？\NNo. It was Grayson, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.61,0:34:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他把这种思想灌输到你脑袋里的么？\NHe put the ideas into your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.27,0:34:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,唆使你来我这的么？\NGoaded you into confronting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.97,0:34:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你冤枉我了\NYou're pointing the gun at the wrong man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.16,0:34:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你看不出他的目的么？\NCan't you see what he's up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.39,0:35:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不论怎样  他赢了  明白了么？\NEither way, he wins. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.40,0:35:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是你杀了我去坐牢\NWhether you kill me and go to jail,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.42,0:35:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我用枪把你当作入侵者杀死\Nor I get a gun and kill you as an intruder,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.54,0:35:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他还是赢了\Nhe still wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.20,0:35:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,赢什么了？  你在说些什么？\NWins what? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.97,0:35:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,想想！  最终谁会留下来\NThink! Who will be left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.87,0:35:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,照顾Murray小姐？\Nto look after Miss Murray?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.61,0:35:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在内心深处  你是知道的。\NYou see, deep down, you know that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.30,0:35:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见过他们在一块\NYou've seen them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.44,0:35:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看向彼此的眼神\NYou've seen the way they look at one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.41,0:35:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜欢她  并且她…\NHe adores her. And she...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.97,0:35:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个天大的笑话！\NThat's a damn lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.12,0:35:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以证明给你看\NI can prove it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.30,0:35:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我指给你看  小心\NLet me show you. Careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.01,0:35:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那个左轮手枪…可能走火\Nthat revolver... it could go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.87,0:35:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我真相\NThen tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.71,0:35:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们背叛你了\NThey've betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.50,0:35:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,最近\NSee, recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.16,0:35:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现Grayson一直在找\NI discovered that Grayson has been searching
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.47,0:35:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一幅画\Nfor one particular painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.61,0:35:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,十年了  他一直在找\NFor 10 years, he's been looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.94,0:35:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,遍布欧洲的每一次拍卖会\Nin every auction and every gallery
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.44,0:35:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,和每一个画廊\Nacross Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.26,0:35:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 停  - 最终他找到了\N- Stop. - And then he found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.83,0:35:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道是因为我从他那把画偷来了\NI know this because I stole it from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.39,0:35:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要动  - 你自己看\N- Don't move. - You'll see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.24,0:35:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他的痴迷远远超出了染料和画布\NHis obsession goes far beyond mere paint and canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.51,0:35:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他雇佣你是为了能靠近她\NHe hires you so that he can get closer to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.55,0:36:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至在他自己家举办你的婚礼\NHe even hosts your engagement party at his own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.62,0:36:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 闭嘴  - 求你了  不要…  这是真的  听着\N- Shut up. - Please, no... it's true. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.82,0:36:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你看   然后你就会明白了\NLet me show you, and then you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.52,0:36:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你就什么都知道了\NThen you'll understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.20,0:36:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,额  天哪  不\NOh, God, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.57,0:36:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Davenport  Davenport…\NDavenport, Davenport...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.98,0:36:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那边那个\NYou there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.61,0:37:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要帮助么？\NYou need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.42,0:37:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你赶紧走\NBest be on your way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.44,0:37:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那再见了\NCheerio, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.93,0:37:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan\NJonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.73,0:38:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么风把你…？\NWhat in the world are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.74,0:38:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有人么\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.70,0:38:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  你一定累坏了吧\NDarling, you must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.88,0:38:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你还没吃饭呢\NI hope you haven't eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.44,0:39:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,厨子为你温着晚餐呢\NThe cook's kept dinner warm for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.85,0:39:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  亲爱的\NThank you, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.72,0:39:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,今天过的怎么样啊？\NHow was your day?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.60,0:39:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会相信的\NYou won't believe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.60,0:39:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我有了确实的证据…\Nbut I have it on good authority that Lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.38,0:39:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的天那  夫人\N- What in God's Name, Mrs.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.90,0:39:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gulliver？- 孩子们  孩子们…\NGulliver? - The children, the children...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.32,0:39:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不见了  他们不见了…\NThey're gone, they're gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.33,0:39:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,额  天哪…\NOh, my God...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.92,0:39:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  女士们  有个人带他们进来了\NSir, ma'am, a man took them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.00,0:39:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.31,0:40:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我告诉你真相…\NYou asked me to tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.58,0:40:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,给我保证\NMade me promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.75,0:40:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就告诉你\NI'll tell it to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.16,0:40:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我初次见你一切都改变了\NNothing has been the same since first I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.73,0:40:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我无法理解的神奇\NYou're a magic beyond my understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.24,0:40:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这是不可能的\NI know it's impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.73,0:40:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你是Ilona  回到我身边\Nbut you are Ilona, come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.53,0:40:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你不止如此\NBut you're more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.91,0:40:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是Mina\NYou are Mina too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.88,0:40:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  我一直隐蔽自己的感情…\NNow, I've tried to keep my feelings close...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.32,0:40:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我做不到\NBut I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.19,0:40:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你已超越我的能力范围\NYou make me want more than I could possibly have.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.99,0:41:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我在阳光下漫步\NYou make me want to walk in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.83,0:41:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我属于你\NI belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.40,0:41:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你属于我\NAnd you belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.71,0:41:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Davenport勋爵死了\NLord Davenport is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.84,0:42:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker先生像你吩咐的那样做了\NMr. Harker worked out just as you planned.
